{"tid":2087404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(集思廣益) 請問做咩先唔犯國安法？","createTime":"2020-06-30T16:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T08:08:17.000Z","uid":7008,"like":70,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"4b7f7b7f22f19dc7b9dfef583abba946f776232c","tid":2087404,"uid":7008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad4ea864df070d11579adecda525b1d8cd1c280","tid":2087404,"uid":86199,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"呼吸"},{"pid":"d56598ef3c89778011a3de2d0cf3e0563826c90e","tid":2087404,"uid":266503,"like":121,"dislike":3,"score":118,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"9549363b611b9a896965c785ea4a8b71c0c7e971","tid":2087404,"uid":332804,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:21:26.000Z","msg":"冇，萬能key黎，中共要入你就入你。"