 be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:51:36.000Z","msg":"拉得"},{"pid":"01fa21770e44d1c492c46d4bec25f263d95e78cb","tid":2087404,"uid":271807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b7f7b7f22f19dc7b9dfef583abba946f776232c","tid":2087404,"uid":7008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T18:00:32.000Z","msg":"正確講，佢無拉你唔代表你無犯法"},{"pid":"0953cb852c1ee1cf04a8a8b6fe6c660877681e79","tid":2087404,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5c6400de59074ef45e6fa9a2bb6279b37d87c6c","tid":2087404,"uid":190296,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:14:51.000Z","msg":"衰啲講句我諗除咗自殺之外其他嘢都係犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為全部野都係用緊國家資源"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T18:13:39.000Z","msg":"自殺仲要逐個死先得<img src=\"/a